      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00001-000-00269"/>Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb967" type="place">Lucerne</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">poste rest.</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb43435" type="place">Suisse</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00001-000-00270"/><rs ref="#pmb513" type="place">Lugano, du Parc</rs>, <date>Sonntag</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>Früh</time>.</dateline></opener><p>Bin über <rs ref="#pmb34007" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Zermatt</hi></rs> und <rs ref="#pmb34011" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Simplon</hi></rs> gut angeko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb513" subtype="implied">wohne</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chön und angenehm. Hoffe<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr auf Nachricht von
               Ihnen und bitte vielmals um Recepi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e der Ta<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>che, das bis jetzt nicht in meinen
               Händen.</p><closer>Ihr <signed>Hugo.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
